dc_description_s: This data layer represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners for Taylor County, Wisconsin in 2019.[Coordinates of PLSS corners supplied by the Taylor County. Data collected by direct observation using survey grade GPS. Coordinates entered manually by GIS Specialist to create GIS point file. PLSS section created and subdivided by GIS Specialist.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
